title: Black Bean Veggie Burgers
content: This is a great veggie burger made with parmesean, crunchy cachews, and chipotle peppers.

title: Tropical Dream Pie
content: From the Moosewood vegetarian cookbook, made of a ginger snap, coconut flake, and pecan crust, a sweetened condensed milk filling with lime juice & zest, and a layer of ripe bananas and mangos.

title: Flourless Almond Cake
content: Like a flourless chocolate cake in that it has many eggs, but made of blanched almond flour

title: Fried Rice
content: The secrets to this simple recipe involve cold, dry, pre-cooked rice, and lots of fresh ginger
